    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "Beacons of warning are placed on every side in the pathway of life to prevent men from approaching the dangerous, forbidden ground; but, notwithstanding this, multitudes choose the fatal path, contrary to the dictates of reason, regardless of God&apos;s law, and in defiance of His vengeance.",
